<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Online Voting Awareness Portal</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f8;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: #34495e;
            padding: 12px;
        }

        nav a {
            background-color: #1abc9c;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 8px 14px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #16a085;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        h1, h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        marquee {
            background-color: #eaf2f8;
            padding: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #1a252f;
        }

        .checkbox-group label {
            display: block;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>🗳️ Online Voting Awareness Portal</h1>
    <p> Supporting one party is Good • But Knowing Your Power great</p>
</header>

<marquee behavior="alternate">
    📢 Your Vote is Your Voice | 🇮🇳 Vote Responsibly | 🔐 Secure Digital Democracy
</marquee>

<nav>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#importance">Importance</a>
    <a href="#process">Process</a>
    <a href="#security">Security</a>
</nav>

<div class="container">

    <div class="card" id="about">
        <h2>📘 About Online Voting</h2>
        <p>
            Online voting allows citizens to cast their votes digitally using secure internet platforms.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" id="importance">
        <h2>⭐ Voter Awareness Checklist</h2>

        <form>
            <div class="checkbox-group">
                <label>
                    <input type="checkbox"> I understand the importance of voting
                </label>
                <label>
                    <input type="checkbox"> I know my vote is confidential
                </label>
                <label>
                    <input type="checkbox"> I will verify election information
                </label>
            </div>

            <br>
            <button type="submit">Confirm Awareness</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="card" id="process">
        <h2>🛠️ Online Voting Process</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Voter Registration</li>
            <li>Identity Verification</li>
            <li>Secure Login</li>
            <li>Vote Casting</li>
            <li>Confirmation ✅</li>
        </ol>

        <button>Learn More</button>
    </div>

    <div class="card" id="security">
        <h2>🔐 Security Measures</h2>
        <p>
            Encryption, authentication, and audit logs ensure vote privacy and prevent fraud.
        </p>

        <p><strong>System Trust Level</strong></p>
        <meter value="0.9">90%</meter>
    </div>

</div>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Online Voting Awareness Portal</p>
    <p>Created by Harrish S</p>
</footer>
<script src = "loginpage.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
